Title: Holed Up
Description:
Oh thank you, thank you, thank you. If you hadn't come along...

Wait! There must be other survivors in the Nook like me!

Please, $c, I beg you. Rescue the rest of my citizens and deliver us safely to Shado-Pan Fallback.
ObjectivesText: Rescue Jin Warmkeg, Ya Firebough, Old Lady Fung, and Sya Zhong.
